Introduction for Business problem ,Capestone Project

Srikanth wants to open his Burger Joint in some Locality of Bangalore, Karnataka.
And he is asking our help in finding the best Locality.

Business Problem 

In order to open Srikanth's burger joint, we will have the need to use some information about the Localities in Bangalore.
We must be sure that the place where the burger joint is opened will have enough customers and also 
that there aren't a large amount of burger joints in the place.
